Core 2: ${color e0e0e0}${font sans:size=7}${execi 8 sensors | grep 'Core 1' | cut -c18-24}${color}${font} | 
Core 3: ${color e0e0e0}${font sans:size=7}${execi 8 sensors | grep 'Core 2' | cut -c18-24}${color}${font} | 
